creator: William Shakespeare
description:
LibriVox recording of The Witches' Brew (MacBeth Act IV Scene I) by William Shakespeare.
Read in English by Ian King; Jason Mills; Julia Niedermaier; Lee Ann Howlett; Laurie Anne Walden; Leonard Wilson; and MaryAnn Spiegel.

Librivox volunteers bring you seven readings of The Witches' Brew from Act IV Scene I of MacBeth, by William Shakespeare. This was the weekly poetry project for October 26, 2014.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (8MB)
